title.narrative: Enhanced local capacity in focus provinces to develop and operationalize local child protection systems and services, including positive parenting, non-violent discipline

description.narrative: The holistic IECD Parenting Programme was successfully rolled out, benefiting about 4,000 children in three focus provinces, Kon Tum, Gia Lai and Dien Bien, through improving parents' and care givers' knowledge and nurturing skills. The government has expressed its commitment to replicate the programme to 15 other provinces, in collaboration with UNICEF. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
